{"tid":203543,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"係街邊洗車 俾人捉","createTime":"2017-04-16T11:03:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-18T20:27:09.000Z","uid":44626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"964bab4a966deec96e17538fe62c782f2035adad","tid":203543,"uid":44626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T11:03:24.000Z","msg":"有冇人中過招？"},{"pid":"38c83f9b5b02cc362c163535820fd1dbc2968544","tid":203543,"uid":10743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T11:59:39.000Z","msg":"捉乜9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26e368230447771d3fa68aab35c90c64521e34ed","tid":203543,"uid":5650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T12:02:03.000Z","msg":"捉鳩你非法排污呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82b307a0a4f7d4e4bb09c2a1eea4fe8005b8283d","tid":203543,"uid":59030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T12:07:28.000Z","msg":"根據香港法例第228章《簡易程序治罪條例》第四條，「在公眾地方犯的妨擾罪等」，當中的細則指，任何人無合法權限或解釋，而將污垢或其他髒物放置在任何公眾地方，或任何排水渠或污水渠內，即屬違法。違者可被罰款500元或監禁三個月。"},{"pid":"383dfdec77e224958270c4bb8c892e2604629fcf","tid":203543,"uid":6363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T12:23:44.000Z","msg":"冇, 不過驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa17febb636215b624bb329115bbc3bc83da9200","tid":203543,"uid":52323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T12:59:53.000Z","msg":"就係你地啲仆街搞到條馬路咁多污水"},{"pid":"062d71d55f7dccf60ab67a6123aba000d47c404c","tid":203543,"uid":53568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T13:19:07.000Z","msg":"雖然係chap.228 section4 但係唔係因為排出污水 係<br />\n<br />\n(10) 在公眾地方殺死、屠宰、展覽、展售(在依法指定作以上用途的市場進行者除外)或餵飼任何馬匹或其他動物而對居民或路人造成煩擾；或為任何馬匹或其他動物釘蹄鐵、放血或治病(發生意外時除外)；或放開、洗擦、梳刷、操練、訓練或馴服任何馬匹或其他動物；<strong>或洗擦、製造或修理車輛的任何部分(發生意外而需就地進行修理者除外)</strong>；<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04b7dacecf80f0f31f38145a49de9effb3e0e18f","tid":203543,"uid":53568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T13:19:53.000Z","msg":"其實好少捉 除非你被人投訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"356575875aafbd1dad4f3e80fb92e67eccf14bfc","tid":203543,"uid":49392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T13:25:09.000Z","msg":"你個樣問題掛，大把的士佬周街洗車都無事"},{"pid":"73d24b7bf4a5b28138777196b74420cd674cfee9","tid":203543,"uid":29291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T13:58:03.000Z","msg":"法例就咁寫 有幾多個真係會捉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n科學園迴旋處長期都係洗車屋"},{"pid":"b2a7f9293fd8237d27d127ceb9c4b5f5eebe032f","tid":203543,"uid":99394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T14:07:17.000Z","msg":"唔好影響到人就得啦，呢個年代搵個位洗車都好撚辛苦"},{"pid":"326dec83f55a83e681eb2d6d886d9cf9065bad08","tid":203543,"uid":53520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T14:30:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你個樣問題掛，大把的士佬周街洗車都無事</blockquote><br />\nd 車行周街整車排到成條街都係好似無聽閶有捉過<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68c8eecfa3924c41871ca30290fe0cb99159f51e","tid":203543,"uid":53520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T14:30:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你個樣問題掛，大把的士佬周街洗車都無事</blockquote><br />\nd 車行周街整車排到成條街都係好似無聽聞有捉過<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"e167c6e37b9901197ad927dd626fef20396d6d68","tid":203543,"uid":60238,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T00:26:40.000Z","msg":"你中午十二點喺彌敦道洗？<br />\n我通常半夜一兩點先出去洗，駁埋水槍慢慢玩，未試過俾人捉"},{"pid":"8d13aec1611c91e423f50394a13a0ab3f4286039","tid":203543,"uid":73123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T00:58:03.000Z","msg":"係錶位場洗車，有差佬黎抄無入錶個d都無理過我<img src=\"/asset