7,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T17:08:44.000Z","msg":"你拎喉洗？ 聽過下好似話因為拎喉洗浪費水源 唔環保所以有條例唔比係街用喉洗車？"},{"pid":"93f07515ff17c3e5f22e9b5e89dcc2469e024c84","tid":203543,"uid":79481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T23:33:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>街洗一定唔比。但上次洗到一半成車泡，警車黎都無捉我，只係開警號坐係到等我沖埋水收野佢就走左，無落charge</blockquote><br />\n都話唔係差佬管<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係食環 好似捉無牌小販都係食環捉唔係差佬捉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n食環可以管，但差佬屎忽痕要做都可以做埋</blockquote><br />\n以我所知差佬係無權捉架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n差佬係無權發票俾你 係食環先有權"},{"pid":"8b0214cf07d28c40657b322132a3daa4b91942fc","tid":203543,"uid":10044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T01:00:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>街洗一定唔比。但上次洗到一半成車泡，警車黎都無捉我，只係開警號坐係到等我沖埋水收野佢就走左，無落charge</blockquote><br />\n有次洗到成車泡 有架警車周到<br />\n叫我即刻走 我話沖埋水先啦 激嬲左佢即刻大鳩我再唔走就抄我牌<br />\n死死氣揸住架成車泡既車走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e4d873d2412ebc61e1ee953c92f3d82b4e01197","tid":203543,"uid":18241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T01:04:42.000Z","msg":"咪罰果幾百蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}